You're lying.
If it's not yours, then whose is it?

232
00:17:14,025 --> 00:17:16,784
Who in this house
reads this kind of novel

233
00:17:16,785 --> 00:17:17,785
besides you kids?

234
00:17:18,945 --> 00:17:19,945
