235
00:17:20,135 --> 00:17:21,915
Well... ahem. Mart.

236
00:17:23,505 --> 00:17:25,265
Just let it go.

237
00:17:25,885 --> 00:17:28,705
I cannot. This is serious.

238
00:17:29,465 --> 00:17:31,105
They'll all go down the wrong path.

239
00:17:31,175 --> 00:17:34,465
What wrong path?
It's just about two men in love.

240
00:17:34,865 --> 00:17:37,065
It's full of dirty scenes.

241
00:17:37,845 --> 00:17:39,865
And you're still kids.

242
00:17:41,025 --> 00:17:42,905
So nobody's going to admit it?

243
00:17:43,015 --> 00:17:45,105
It really isn't ours.

244
00:17:45,135 --> 00:17:46,265
That's right.

245
00:17:46,525 --> 00:17:48,945
Fine. In that case,

246
