247
00:17:51,145 --> 00:17:52,115
- What?
- What?

248
00:17:52,145 --> 00:17:54,784
Auntie Mart, it's not ours. Honest.

249
00:17:54,785 --> 00:17:56,665
- That's not fair.
- Mom, come on.

250
00:17:56,685 --> 00:17:57,435
Mart. Mart.

251
00:17:57,455 --> 00:17:58,255
Ahem.

252
00:17:58,275 --> 00:17:59,165
Come here.

253
00:17:59,185 --> 00:18:00,705
What is it, Father?

254
00:18:00,945 --> 00:18:02,065
Just come here.

255
00:18:02,585 --> 00:18:03,585
What is this?

256
00:18:05,725 --> 00:18:08,704
- Oh come on.
- That's so unfair, Auntie Mart.

257
00:18:08,705 --> 00:18:09,705
Hold on.

258
00:18:10,305 --> 00:18:11,725
If it's not ours,

259
00:18:12,675 --> 00:18:13,905
then who does it belong to?

260
00:18:14,135 --> 00:18:15,225
Yeah, whose book?

261
00:18:28,465 --> 00:18:30,065
- Father.
- Hmm.

262
00:18:30,235 --> 00:18:32,465
Please don't make this
harder for me.

263
00:18:32,535 --> 00:18:33,975
I have to punish them.

264
00:18:34,415 --> 00:18:37,665
That's enough. Leave them alone.

265
00:18:38,375 --> 00:18:40,465
But they broke the rules.

266
00:18:40,865 --> 00:18:42,105
Let it go this once.

267
00:18:42,945 --> 00:18:45,625
What is going on?
This isn't like you at all.

268
00:18:46,065 --> 00:18:48,865
It doesn't matter.
They are getting punished.

269
00:18:49,165 --> 00:18:50,385
Mart. Mart.

270
00:18:51,625 --> 00:18:53,665
That book is mine.

271
00:18:54,265 --> 00:18:55,265
I'm sorry.

272
00:18:55,295 --> 00:18:57,685
This book. It belongs to me.

273
00:18:58,075 --> 00:18:59,465
